{"type": "article", "id": 12684, "title": "自由伸缩的咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-28T07:28:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071225066wlju4tVUCkeQaZI.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自纽约的艺术家 Ian Stell 最近做了一个可以根据用户的需求自由伸缩的咖啡桌，桌子名为 “Sinan”，平行于地面的横格子由橡木制成，而支撑部分则采用了黄铜材料，一横一竖，构成巧妙的铰接格子，可以流畅地进行大小的变换。这是<a href=\"http://www.ianstell.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看他的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140402xS3u7lOvNo85tsED.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140405bVjmHAGkQpSLuvnT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140406cukf1EnLPtS8yVx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404062oUmdhZCplvqBEse.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}